org.opendaylight.controller.forwardingrulesmanager

Class FlowEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.forwardingrulesmanager.FlowEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class FlowEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a flow applications request Forwarding Rules Manager to install on a network node. A FlowEntry is constituted of a flow (match + actions), the target network node, and the flow name. It also includes a group name. For instance the flows constituting a policy all share the same group name.
